sentence: what airlines have flights from baltimore to seattle
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.airline_code||'"', '"'||v2.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v3.city_code||'"', '"'||v3.city_name||'"', '"'||v4.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v5.city_code||'"', '"'||v5.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v1.flight_id||'"' FROM airline v0, flight v1,
 airport_service v2, city v3, airport_service v4, city v5 
WHERE ((v0.airline_code = ANY v1.airline_code) AND (((v1.from_airport = ANY v2.airport_code) 
AND ((v2.city_code = ANY v3.city_code) 
AND (v3.city_name = 'BALTIMORE'))) AND ((v1.to_airport = ANY v4.airport_code) 
AND ((v4.city_code = ANY v5.city_code) 
AND (v5.city_name = 'SEATTLE')))));
